1.3 “You” or “Licensee” means the individual or entity using the Software.
1.4 “Local Game Store” or “LGS” means a brick-and-mortar retail store primarily engaged
    in tabletop gaming products/events, operating in the Philippines.
1.5 “Tournament Use” means using the Software to organize, manage, score, and report
    tournament rounds and standings for in-store or store-run events.
1.6 “Redistribute” means to sell, resell, license, sublicense, rent, lease, lend, publish,
